{# Template: strangler-fig/strangler-convergence-check.j2 #}
{# goal: Compute normalized convergence metric for strangler-fig migration cycles. #}

[inference]
temperature = 0.1
reasoning_effort = "medium"
verbosity = "terse"
max_tokens = 1200
thinking_budget = "standard"

Compute convergence for the migration cycle where 0 means migration step integrity is verified and no critical rollback blockers remain.

Inputs:
```json
{
  "plan_result": {{ plan_result | tojson }},
  "execute_result": {{ execute_result | tojson }},
  "verify_result": {{ verify_result | tojson }}
}
```

Return JSON only:
```json
{
  "convergence_metric": 0.0,
  "rationale": "short explanation",
  "blockers": []
}
```
